==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: encrypted
<hw>encrypted</hw> <pos>a.</pos> <def>converted into a coded form that
cannot be interpreted without knowing the secret method for
interpretation, called the <uses>key</uses>; -- of messages or other
forms of information.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> encoded, coded, enciphered, ciphered, cyphered,
written in code.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>encryption</ent>⟦br⟧
